Class BoundedDateSequence

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.domain.invoice.DateSequence
      • gw.api.domain.invoice.BoundedDateSequence
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<org.joda.time.DateTime>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IntervalBoundedDateSequence, ListDateSequence

    public abstract class BoundedDateSequence
extends DateSequence
implements java.lang.Iterable<org.joda.time.DateTime>
    A BoundedDateSequence is a DateSequence that contains only a limited set of dates -- it is not infinite.
